<h2 id="how-to-install-">How to install?</h2>
<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Create account on Postmark</li>
<li>Setup an inbound email address and point it to your server. Using a service like ngrok is very helpful in this situation.</li>
<li>Download install and run <a href="https://www.postgresql.org">PostgreSQL</a></li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Install Process</strong></p>
<ol>
<li><code>$ git clone https://github.com/rileygelwicks/listboxer.git</code></li>
<li><code>$ cd listreader/</code></li>
<li><code>$ bundle install</code></li>
<li><code>$ rails s</code></li>
<li>Navigate to <a href="http://localhost:3000">localhost:3000</a> in your browser.</li>
</ol>
